value.snippet: To find your correct build number: Launch Microsoft Edge. Open the Settings and more (...) menu, choose Help and feedback, and then choose About Microsoft Edge. deepLinks.name: Documentation
deepLinks.snippet: Manage and configure the Edge WebDriver service. When you create a new EdgeDriver object to start a Microsoft Edge session, Selenium launches a new Edge WebDriver process that the EdgeDriver object communicates with.
